  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a world of magic and adventure in the world of Aritas and defeat the Demon Lord! Play alone in singleplayer or with friends on LAN!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383930/extras/a8dac694f337a6b74f4e83bf4d7f8025.avif?t=1735236901\" width=800 height=141 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 3 playable races! Customize your character's hair color and eye color! Choose one of three classes: Warrior, Holy Knight, and Dreadcaster!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383930/extras/a76c8070840560c95034d47cccf0a8de.avif?t=1735236901\" width=800 height=141 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow one of two main questlines, explore the dungeons, or do sidequests! Level up your character and discover hidden boxes of loot in the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a world of magic and adventure in the world of Aritas and defeat the Demon Lord! Play alone in singleplayer or with friends on LAN!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383930/extras/a8dac694f337a6b74f4e83bf4d7f8025.avif?t=1735236901\" width=800 height=141 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 3 playable races! Customize your character's hair color and eye color! Choose one of three classes: Warrior, Holy Knight, and Dreadcaster!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383930/extras/a76c8070840560c95034d47cccf0a8de.avif?t=1735236901\" width=800 height=141 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow one of two main questlines, explore the dungeons, or do sidequests! Level up your character and discover hidden boxes of loot in the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
